There are two ways to build/install this package

1. Using the original Makefile

	To build

		type 'makel make obint

	To install

		stall with 'make install'

2. Using cmake

	To build

		You will want to build in a dieectory other rgan the original
		source directory, otherwise cmake will overwrite the original
		Makefile.

		mkdir build
		cd build
		cmake ..

		make

	To install

		make install

	To create Debian package

		cpack

	To install debian package

		dpkg -i link11-0.1.1-Linux.deb

